channel.title: Electronic Cleanliness
channel.description:
Apparently I don't have it.. My laptop has been over heating for the last year so I finally opened it up to assess the situation only to find this in between my fan and its vent to let out hot air:
[url=http://a.imagehost.org/view/0573/IMG00345][img]http://a.imagehost.org/0573/IMG00345.jpg[/img][/url]
That was clogging the entire vent... Laptop is running like a champ now and it doesn't burn my legs anymore or spontaneously shut down!
Moral: Clean your shit more often.
